# Task Progress Checklist

- [ ] Open http://localhost:3001/tasks
- [ ] Check left sidebar for overlaps (Search vs Document list)
- [ ] Select or create a document
- [ ] Check middle editor area background (no buggy stripes/dots)
- [ ] Check right sidebar "DÖKÜMAN BİLGİSİ" for overlaps
- [ ] Click "Görev Ekle", type "Test Görevi", and add it
- [ ] Verify the task appears in the list
- [ ] Take a final screenshot of the state
